window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A multi-dimensional entity, known as The Scribe, is on a mission to unravel all of Creation.</p> <p>The Scribe has his mind set on the Cosmic Clock, as it counts down to another Great Reset. As the epitome of chaos and a purveyor of purpose, it is only fitting that he does what he was created to do; to cause a chain reaction that would undo all of Creation.</p> <p>But his plan faces an obstacle in the form of two 2,000-year-old archenemies, Shi'mon and Yehuda, who must find a way to bury the hatchet and save humanity from certain extinction at the hands of the soulless creatures created by The Scribe known as...The Bright Eyes!</p>"; 
